{"tid":355821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖慎入] 俄羅斯醉男跨欄 下體鈎住整個撕裂","createTime":"2017-08-11T15:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T07:09:21.000Z","uid":28053,"like":23,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08214a06bad5077ee2235857f0f13c6d9787aa82","tid":355821,"uid":28053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:09:15.000Z","msg":"男人最痛！俄羅斯奔薩州庫茲涅茨克一名27歲醉酒男子日前圖攀越金屬圍欄卡在，於是直接往下跳，不幸將整個下體撕裂，掛在圍欄上面。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方證實，欄杆上的人體組織確實是男子的生殖器官，男子爬過金屬圍欄時發生血腥意外，整個生殖器官血淋淋地被欄杆鈎住，懸掛在半空中。<br />\n<br />\n而男子躍下後痛心疾首地奔向附近醫院求救，經醫生緊急縫合後，暫時沒有生命危險。不過由於整個生殖器官被強行撕裂，無法重新接駁，男子無奈痛失「寶貝」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/475092-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%86%89%E7%94%B7%E8%B7%A8%E6%AC%84+%E4%B8%8B%E9%AB%94%E9%88%8E%E4%BD%8F%E6%95%B4%E5%80%8B%E6%92%95%E8%A3%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F475092-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E9%2586%2589%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E6%25AC%2584%2B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%25AB%2594%25E9%2588%258E%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%2595%25B4%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%2592%2595%25E8%25A3%2582&d=UoN0GoyRNBB3A0DgAsL9usPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=7c1af542\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F475092-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E9%2586%2589%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E6%25AC%2584%2B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%25AB%2594%25E9%2588%258E%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%2595%25B4%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%2592%2595%25E8%25A3%2582&h=45ed222d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/475092-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%86%89%E7%94%B7%E8%B7%A8%E6%AC%84+%E4%B8%8B%E9%AB%94%E9%88%8E%E4%BD%8F%E6%95%B4%E5%80%8B%E6%92%95%E8%A3%82</a>"},{"pid":"568fac705f63ca53858696851a6c53975c0ab9f3","tid":355821,"uid":51978,"like"